# Optional configuration for powerbi-mcp.
# Copy to ".env" and adjust, or set these as real environment variables.

# Pin the server to a single Azure AD tenant (GUID or domain).
# Leave unset to allow any work/school account ("organizations").
# POWERBI_TENANT_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

# Use your own app registration instead of the default public client.
# POWERBI_CLIENT_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
